<div id="getting-involved" class="container-fluid bg-dark text-white">
  <div class="row justify-content-center py-5">
    <div class="col-3 pb-4">
      <h2 class="text-center underline"><strong>VOLUNTEER</strong></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100"></div>

    <!-- Form Selector -->
    <div class="col-6">
      <label for="formDropdown">Choose a Way to Assist from the Dropdown Menu:</label>
      <select id="formDropdown" class="form-control mb-5 volunteerFormSelector" data-target=".subForm">
        <option value="host" data-show=".host">Host A Soldier</option>
        <option value="sponsor" data-show=".sponsor">Corporate Sponsorships</option>
        <option value="donate" data-show=".donate">Individual Donation</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100"></div>

    <!-- Host a Soldier Form -->
    <div class="col-6 d-none host subForm">
      <h3>HOST A SOLDIER</h3>
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="hostingName">Full Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="hostingName" aria-describedby="hostingNameHelp" placeholder="Enter Full Name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="hostingInputEmail">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="hostingInputEmail" aria-describedby="hostingEmailHelp" placeholder="Enter email">
          <small id="hostingEmailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="hostingFormControlTextarea">Message</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="hostingFormControlTextarea" rows="3" placeholder="How would you like to help?"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100"></div>

    <!-- Corporate Sponsorship Form -->
    <div class="col-6 d-none sponsor subForm">
      <h3>CORPORATE SPONSORSHIP</h3>
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="corporateSponsorshipName">Full Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="corporateSponsorshipName" aria-describedby="corporateSponsorshipNameHelp" placeholder="Enter Full Name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="corporateSponsorshipInputEmail">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="corporateSponsorshipInputEmail1" aria-describedby="corporateSponsorshipEmailHelp" placeholder="Enter email">
          <small id="corporateSponsorshipEmailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="corporateSponsorshipFormControlTextarea">Message</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="corporateSponsorshipFormControlTextarea" rows="3" placeholder="How would you like to help?"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="w-100"></div>

    <!-- Individual Donation Form -->
    <div class="col-6 d-none donate subForm">
      <h3>INDIVIDUAL DONATION</h3>
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="donationName">Full Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="donationName" aria-describedby="donationNameHelp" placeholder="Enter Full Name">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="donationInputEmail">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" class="form-control" id="donationInputEmail1" aria-describedby="donationEmailHelp" placeholder="Enter email">
          <small id="donationHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="donationFormControlTextarea">Message</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="donationFormControlTextarea1" rows="3" placeholder="How would you like to help?"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-info">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>



  </div>
</div>

<div id="meet-the-soldiers" class="container-fluid">
  <h2 class="py-5 text-center underline"><strong>MEET THE SOLDIERS</strong></h2>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-6">
      <p class="text-justify">
      What started off as a local initiative of the New York Upper East Side Jewish
      community has now become a global movement, dedicated to helping veterans of the 
      IDF reintegrate into civilian life with the love and support they need to thrive. 
      In 2018, a south Florida trip sparked an inititive by the Las Olas Chabbad due 
      to the passion and Jewish and Israeli values of our community. We are honored 
      to bring another twelve wounded Israeli soldiers in 2019 to our community for 
      a warm embrace and healing - South Florida style.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-6">
      <div class="container-fluid">
        <h3 class="text-center underline pt-5">Learn About Our Impact on Our 2018 Soldiers</h3>
        <div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
